"author_information": "William Shakespeare (1564-1616) was an English playwright, poet, and actor, widely regarded as the greatest writer in the English language and the world's greatest dramatist.",
"interesting_fact": "The story of *Romeo and Juliet* was not original to Shakespeare. It was based on an Italian tale, which had been translated into English verse as *The Tragical History of Romeus and Juliet* by Arthur Brooke in 1562. Shakespeare, however, transformed the story with his poetic genius and dramatic skill, making it a timeless masterpiece."
